Halep had not lost a set in her previous two meetings with Kontaveit, who managed just one breakpoint on the former world number one’s serve. The Romanian, runner-up at Melbourne Park in 2018, will meet either Spaniard Garbine Muguruza or Anastasia Pavlyuchenkova of Russia for a place in Saturday’s final. (Reporting by Sudipto Ganguly; editing by Peter Rutherford) Please note you must be a Maverick Insider to comment. Sign up here or sign in if you are already an Insider.